he whole design system is documented and available online. You can find everything about components, tokens, guidelines and principles of OUDS.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"icon finder","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" is also available there to get icons for your projects.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"step","code":null},{"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-3.png","code":null,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDS iOS provides also a wiki attached to its GitHub repository. The wiki is a public base of knowledge with plenty of things: available API, technicala architecture, tips about processes, tests, conventions and toolings.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Have a look "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" to discover how OUDS works."}]}],"runtimePreview":null},{"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-4.png","code":null,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For technical reasons the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository does not embed the source code of the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"design system toolbox","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" app. In fact this app and all its snapshots for tests increases a lot the size of the repository."}]}],"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To get the source code of this showcase app, go to its dedicated GitHub repository at "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios-design-system-toolbox","isActive":true}]}],"runtimePreview":null},{"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-5.png","code":null,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS is open source, public and uses GitHub as forge. Thus, you will find common things inside the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository."}]}],"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Do not hesitate to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/issues","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/discussions","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"!"}]}],"runtimePreview":null}],"anchor":"More-resources","title":"More resources","contentSection":[{"kind":"contentAndMedia","mediaPosition":"trailing","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Xcode can use the Swift DocC documentation of OUDS, and this documentation is used to build a static web site.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"But there are also other resources which can be useful for you.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-discovery-6-going-further"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-discovery-5-styling-things#Want-to-be-an-artist":{"abstract":[{"text":"Even if components increase the identity of your apps, it is not enough. Typography, fonts and tokens are here to improve that.","type":"text"}],"title":"Want to be an artist?","url":"\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-discovery-5-styling-things#Want-to-be-an-artist","role":"pseudoSymbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-5-styling-things#Want-to-be-an-artist","type":"section","kind":"section"},"https://github.com/Orange-OpenSource/ouds-ios/issues":{"type":"link","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Ora